{"tid":51451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視派聖誕禮物 港60員工接「大信封」","createTime":"2016-12-23T08:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T14:16:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"398a1f13985e92eea01693497ef22a96684fc00b","tid":51451,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161223/280pix/1482481728_f9e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161223%2F280pix%2F1482481728_f9e3.jpg&h=89c0241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂視資金屢傳出現問題，本報獲消息指，樂視香港於平安夜前夕，裁員60人。<br />\n<br />\n本報就此向樂視查詢，發言人指，公司現進入「營運和管理優化階段」，是次架構重組是公司業務發展的正常過程；又指，架構重組屬一次性，相關員工可獲得按照香港僱傭條例規定的員工離職補償。樂視表示，現有業務和會員服務將不會受到任何影響。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又引述樂視控股亞太區總裁、LeEco香港CEO高峻早前接受媒體專訪時曾表示，LeEco正在進行亞太區、香港及LeSports Hong Kong三大板塊的融合，相應的組織架構也需要重整，以進一步優化業務模式、提升營運效益。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒《懶熊體育》月初引述消息稱，樂視體育內部已决定整體裁員，幅度將達到20%，其中智能硬件部門的裁員幅度高達50%；於今年5月11日先加盟的樂視體育總編輯敖銘，據悉已遞交信辭職，至離職日只上任短短7個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56084107&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56084107%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161223&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e94dc8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56084107%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161223&h=74602a71\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56084107&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161223</a>"},{"pid":"204e61a55267920d3204cb70710e871290b3035b","tid":51451,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"正丫，新年前炒人真係識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cl